Factory Method:
Problem: Ingredients can be shared among other regional US franchise. Furthermore,
it would assure that the ingredients they get have the high quality. In relation to
programming, if all regional US franchise would share the same ingredients, then it
is easier to maintain, modify, and even extend. All different types of pizza share
the same set of ingredient they just differ in what type of cheese, sauce, and dough,
and other additional add-ons such as veggies, or if it has meat like pepperoni and
clams.

